<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.9">
<l>amarar toḻappaṭu vāṉai yaṉaittula kukkum pirāṉai</l>
<l>yamarar maṉattiṉuḷ yōku puṇarntavaṉ ṟaṉṉō ṭoṉṟāka</l>
<l>vamarat tuṇiyaval lārka ḷoḻiyaval lātava rellā</l>
<l>mamara niṉainteḻun tāṭi yalaṟṟuva tēkaru mammē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for those capable of suitably resolving to be one with him</l>
<l>joining the yoga in the mind of the immortals on the lord of the whole world,</l>
<l>the one who is praised by the immortals, of all the others besides</l>
<l>suitably thinking, rising, dancing and babbling is the only action.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
